Description:
    Creates Phlex views via the standard Rails scaffold generator

Example:
    bin/rails generate scaffold article title:string --template-engine=phlex_scaffold

This particular generator will create:
	app/views/articles/article_view.rb
	app/views/articles/edit_view.rb
	app/views/articles/form.rb
	app/views/articles/index_view.rb
	app/views/articles/new_view.rb
	app/views/articles/show_view.rb

other files produced are the result of other generators